        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is AWeber good for beginners with no email marketing experience?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. AWeber is one of the most beginner-friendly platforms available. The interface is intuitive, templates are ready to customize, and their 24/7 customer support (including phone) means you're never stuck. You can have your first landing page and welcome email live within 30 minutes of signing up.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I sell digital products directly through AWeber?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes! AWeber includes built-in payment processing through their Pages & Payments feature. Create a landing page, add your product, connect your payment method, and start selling. No need for separate checkout tools like Stripe or Gumroad. It handles everything from the sales page to delivery emails.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does AWeber compare to other email marketing tools for small businesses?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AWeber's biggest advantages are deliverability (they consistently rank among the highest), 27 years of experience (they invented the autoresponder), transparent pricing, and exceptional customer support. While other tools may offer more flashy features, AWeber excels at doing the fundamentals extremely well—which matters most when you're building a business.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Does AWeber offer a free plan?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. AWeber's free plan supports up to 500 subscribers and includes landing pages, email templates, basic automations, and 24/7 support. It's one of the most generous free plans in the industry and perfect for getting started without any financial commitment.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
